description:
This is a 30 minute workout called '30 Min CALISTHENICS WORKOUT | No Equipment | DAY 1' from the channel Tom Peto Training.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Ready for Day 1 of my Calisthenics series? This is a 30 minute Calisthenics workout with no equipment needed you can follow along at home. This routine is designed to build muscle, increase strength and develop flexibility. The full body workout includes beginner Calisthenics exercises, as well as more advanced variations making it suitable for a range of abilities.
